newsitem.title: FINLAND: NOKIA ADR ENDS DOWN AT $45-1/8 (FIM 205.85).
newsitem.headline: NOKIA ADR ENDS DOWN AT $45-1/8 (FIM 205.85).

text.p: Nokia's A share ADR closed $1-1/8 down at $45-1/8 in New York on Wednesday.
Its Wall Street closing equals about 205.85 markka. In Helsinki on Wednesday, Nokia A closed down 1.70 markka at 209.00.
Valmet's ADR (two shares) closed $0-3/8 hihger at $32-3/4 on Wall Street. The price equals about 74.70 markka. In Helsinki, Valmet closed down 0.50 markka at 74.00.
Rauma's ADR was untraded in New York on Wednesday after closing up $0-1/8 at $20-3/8 on Tuesday.
Rauma closed flat at 92.00 markka in Helsinki.
